MILFS CLI gateway. Enter 'help' for commands, 'exit' to quit.
> Available commands:
  help                      - show this help
  mkdir <path>              - create directory
  create <path>             - create empty file
  write <path> <data>       - write data to file
  cat <path>                - print file contents
  read <path>               - same as cat
  ls [path]                 - list directory contents (default: /)
  exit                      - exit program
